         Notes:

    A little over a year ago the doors to the Mental Asylum were swung open by
    label boss Indecent Noise creating a new home for everything dark, twisted
    and up tempo in trance and tech trance. After 17 hugely successful releases
    in the first 12 months from various artists, Indecent Noise presents the
    label's first ever compilation CD. "Tales From The Mental Asylum: Chapter 1"
    showcases all the best releases and remixes from the labels first year
    including material not only from the label head himself but from artists
    such as Will Atkinson, Jordan Suckley, Bowdidge & Taylor, Eddie Bitar and
    many more.

    Enjoy!
